    <body><p><seg rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
御書拝見仕候。明日西役所え云云の由、早<seg facs="../../../gaiji/1-02/1-02-22.png" rend="gaiji" rendition="img" source="※(二の字点、1-2-22)" />参上の筈ニ候得ども、蒸気船借入且手銃千<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">廷</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（挺）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>取入申候て早<seg facs="../../../gaiji/1-02/1-02-22.png" rend="gaiji" rendition="img" source="※(二の字点、1-2-22)" />出帆と決心仕候ニ付、通弁者其外、人数をそろへ異館へ参候所ナリ。今宵彼方より帰次第御旅宿まで参上仕候。謹言。<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">六日</seg>
<seg rend="jisage_1" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em">佐々木先生<seg rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">楳拝</seg></seg>
<seg rend="jisage_6" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 6em">左右</seg>
<lb />
<lb />
